data.description: This gorgeous home sits on over 3 beautiful acres, with 4 bedrooms and 2 baths. There are 2 large living rooms with the open concept kitchen. The master bedroom has a large master bath complete with tub and separate shower! This home has over 2000 sq. ft. and it's all on one floor. The large pantry will provide needed storage room for all of your cooking needs and the utility room leads out to the back yard, making it convenient to enter when outside doing yard work. You can enjoy over 3 (mostly wooded) acres and country living.
